flowchart TD
    A([PipelineRunner._run_doit called]) --> B{Any MOJO steps\nin pipeline?}

    B -- No --> C[Batch doit dispatch\npython -m doit run pipeline]
    C --> D[_sync_step_records\nread marker files]
    D --> E([Return result.json])

    B -- Yes --> F[Run steps individually\nin step_index order]

    F --> G{step_type?}

    G -- NOTEBOOK --> H[doit run single step\npython -m doit run task_name]
    H --> I[_sync_step_records\nfor this step only]
    I --> J{More steps?}

    G -- MOJO --> K[_dispatch_mojo_step\nPOST /execute to mojo-compute]
    K --> L{HTTP response\nstatus?}
    L -- ok --> M[Update ExecutionStep\nstatus=COMPLETED\ncompleted_at=now]
    M --> J
    L -- error --> N[Update ExecutionStep\nstatus=FAILED\nerror_message from response]
    N --> O([Raise RuntimeError])

    J -- Yes --> G
    J -- No --> P[_read_result_json\nfrom S3]
    P --> E

    style C fill:#d4edda
    style H fill:#d4edda
    style K fill:#cce5ff
    style O fill:#f8d7da
